<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Search for anything</b></p><p>Press <span class="shortcut">Shift</span> twice to open the <span class="control">Search Everywhere</span> popup.</p><p>It lets you find any element of your source code, a file, an action, a UI element, or even a Git commit.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/tips_search_everywhere.png" alt="Search Everywhere" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>